defaultThe fund’s 
defaultfiduciary responsibility 
defaultis to act 
defaultin the best 
defaultinterest of its members. T
defaulthe Fund 
defaultmanagement 
defaultrecognises that financially material environmental issues, e.g. climate change
default,
default can adversely impact on the Fund's financial risks and investment returns and thus should be taken into account in the investment strategy. Accordingly, the Fund has integrated the consideration of environmental, social and governance 
default(ESG) 
defaultissues throughout the funding and investment decision making process.
