defaultWORKING WITH OTHERSdefault&#xa0;
default5.1
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultWe
default will normally act through partnerships and alliances with other institutional pension funds, shareholder bodies, and asset owner organisation
defaults, but we reserve the right to act independently.
default This will include the UNPRI, the Institutional Investors Group on Climate Change (IIGCC) and the UK Sustainable Investment and Finance Association (UKSIF).  To further support the integration of environmental governance, we are 
defaultsignatories to the Investor Statement on Climate Change, the Carbon Disclosure Project (CDP) and its sister projects, the Water Disclosure Project (WDP) and the Forestry Footprint Disclosure Project (FFDP).
